    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing my pride and joy. Honestly, this car is a total dream\u2014it's in such incredible, pristine condition that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives as smooth as silk. You really have to see this beauty in person to appreciate how flawless it is. I'm looking for a great new home for it, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
