      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
