    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit is mechanically flawless, boasting a perfectly linear power delivery through its six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed to the highest standards, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement with structural plates. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, supported by an unblemished suspension geometry and M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The exterior and interior are in concours condition, showing zero signs of thermal cycling fatigue or mechanical wear. This is a turn-key collector specimen for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
